title: Pakistan: Suicide bomber rams explosive-laden vehicle into security post in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa; 12 killed
summary_full: A suicide bombing and attack by gunmen on a security post in Pakistan's Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province resulted in the deaths of 11 soldiers and a child. Security forces thwarted the overnight breach attempt, later killing 12 TTP militants. The explosives-laden vehicle also damaged civilian homes, injuring seven others.
